data.description: Come home to this nicely renovated 3bdrms, 2baths home!! Come experience the finishes of a high end home all for under $210,000!! This home has a fully renovated kitchen featuring custom cabinets with soft close drawers, granite counters, and updated appliances!! The bathrooms were also renovated in 2020 to include a tiled shower in the primary bathroom. Are you worried about the hot water heater?? It’s less than 3 years old as well. Oh the roof was replaced with architectural shingles in 2018 too…Did I miss anything?? I think the only thing missing is YOU!! Make this house your home today!!
